Boxing star Ricky Hatton asks the Fifth Gear team to pimp his ride 
Tim Shaw finds out whether the price is right when it comes to expensive 
tyres. Vicki-Butler Henderson and Tiff Needell challenge each other to 
an off-road duel; Tom Ford reviews the revolutionary new Ford Fiesta 
and Jonny Smith attempts to bring the classic Volkswagen Golf GTI Mk2 
into the 21st century - with mixed success
